title: Delicious pumpkin pecan pie
ingredients: ['Filling', '2 eggs', '4 tablespoons brown sugar', '300ml condensed sweetened milk', '400g pumpkin puree', '2 tablespoons plain flour', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '125g pecan halves', 'Pastry', '250g plain flour', '1 teaspoon salt', '150g chilled butter, cubed', '60ml water']
